        "share_text": "An extraordinary evening with @shopmarissacollections celebrating their distinguished partnership with the timeless and iconic house of @davidwebbjewels. \n\nIt was a true honor to be styled by David, the company\u00e2\u0080\u0099s Head of Sales, in a singular serpent masterpiece - a one-of-a-kind creation featured on the acclaimed series The White Lotus. \n\nExquisite in its craftsmanship, the piece took ten months to create from scratch as each scale was hand assembled and it features rare and precious Colombian diamonds and emeralds throughout. \n\nI was also adorned in a remarkable vintage convertible design - a versatile treasure that transforms effortlessly from choker to elongated necklace and bracelet - a testament to the house\u00e2\u0080\u0099s enduring innovation.\n\nThis was an evening I will forever cherish \u00e2\u0080\u0094 one defined by heritage, beauty, and the rare privilege of wearing pieces that transcend adornment and become story.\n\nA sculptural frog earring completed the ensemble and swiftly became an undeniable must-have for me \u00e2\u0080\u0094 an emblem of whimsy, strength, and artistry, reimagined with a modern sensibility.\n\nMy deepest gratitude to my esteemed styling advisor, @susan_marissacollections, whom I have had the pleasure of working with for many years and countless meaningful occasions. Her discernment, grace, and unwavering eye for excellence continue to make her my most trusted ally on Palm Beach Island for all matters of style.\n\nOutfit Details:\n\u00e2\u0080\u00a2 Dress: @alc_ltd @shopmarissacollections \n\u00e2\u0080\u00a2 Jewelry: @davidwebbjewels \n\u00e2\u0080\u00a2 Handbag: Bottega Veneta \n\u00e2\u0080\u00a2 Shoes: Bottega Veneta",
